{
  "stem": "22391.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that was for two days, we were in the thing because at one point, they were going to take us through [NON-ENGLISH] to go to Germany.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And by that time, they borders sort of were closed, so now they had to take us back to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were right near Vienna-- Sopron is like very close by to Vienna.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But they tried to circle us around to stay longer in the cattle cars and hopefully die.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then finally, we got to, to the Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, we never saw grandfather, but we-- we were together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was my aunt-- my father's single sister-- my mother, and my father and my sister and brother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we got to Birkenau and somebody told us that the hospital group where my grandfather is, it's the fourth cattle car down.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I started to look there to look-- to see--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, it was so many people that you couldn't walk too far.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I just wanted to see my grandfather.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as they were telling us where the car is where my grandfather is, I saw them turning them onto an open truck.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were throwing all the people from the car to the truck.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got-- I started to cry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And while I was turning down and crying, I lost my parents and everybody.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By time I came to myself to look for them, my father and my brother and my sister, everybody was gone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then I remember my mother had a new coat, so I went back to the car to take out her new coat to take with me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was hoping someplace we're going to meet yet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And of course that had never happened.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
